---
// /brands/garland-range-repair/, Cluster 08 Stove/Range. Garland combo + US Range sibling coverage.
// Welbilt → Ali Group July 2022. Legacy 301 inherited from cluster 07 /garland-commercial-ovens-repair/ (14 imp).
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import BrandBranchesGrid from '../../components/BrandBranchesGrid.astro';
import { MAIN_PHONE, MAIN_PHONE_TEL } from '../../data/branches';

const title = "Garland Range Repair | Southern California, M-Series, G-Series Steakhouse";
const description = "Garland M/G series heavy-duty range + Charbroiler repair Southern California. Welbilt→Ali Group. steakhouse standard. $120. (424) 325-0520.";
const canonical = "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/garland-range-repair/";

const faqs = [
  { q: "Who owns Garland?", a: "Garland Group has been part of Ali Group since July 2022, when Ali Group completed its acquisition of Welbilt Inc. (Garland's previous parent). Garland is headquartered in Mississauga, Ontario, Canada (historically Freeland, Pennsylvania) and has manufactured commercial cooking equipment since 1864, making it one of the oldest continuously-operating commercial range makers in North America. Post-2022, Garland is an Ali Group NA sibling to Pitco and Frymaster fryers (cluster 06), Champion and CMA dishwashers (cluster 05), Manitowoc ice machines (cluster 03), Beverage-Air refrigeration (cluster 02), Kolpak/Master-Bilt/Nor-Lake walk-ins (cluster 01), and Montague (cluster 07 + 08)." },
  { q: "What's the difference between Garland M-series and G-series?", a: "M-series is electric; G-series is gas. Both are Garland's heavy-duty restaurant range lines, sized across different burner counts and oven-compartment configurations for different kitchen scales. For LA steakhouse operations, G-series gas ranges are the substantial majority of the install base, gas-fired heavy-duty ranges deliver the burner intensity that steakhouse cooking demands. M-series electric ranges appear at kitchens without commercial gas supply or where operators specifically prefer electric cooking. Plus MCO-E (electric) and MCO-GS (gas) convection ranges, S680B/S684B hardcore heavy-duty units, and Garland Charbroilers GS-series (steakhouse signature, infrared burner grills separate from the main range line)." },
  { q: "Does Garland still make commercial ovens, or is that only the range line now?", a: "Garland makes both ranges and range-oven combinations (ranges with oven compartments below). The company's primary product category is commercial ranges, that's why cluster 08 Commercial Stove/Range owns this combo per the tree-primary-product routing rule. Legacy WP URL `/garland-commercial-ovens-repair/` (from the earlier WP site) picked up both \"garland range repair\" and \"garland oven repair\" queries because the range-oven combination is the dominant Garland product form in the installed base. Cluster 07 Commercial Ovens intentionally did not write a separate Garland oven combo, queries route here to cluster 08 per the cross-cluster routing architecture." },
  { q: "What is US Range, and why is it covered on this Garland page?", a: "US Range is Garland's sibling brand under the same Welbilt → Ali Group family. Both brands share parts supply infrastructure, service network, and operational heritage. Rather than writing a separate US Range combo page, we cover the US Range product line in this Garland page, the sibling relationship means service for US Range equipment flows through the same Ali Group parts chain and follows the same diagnostic approach as Garland. US Range C836-series and R60/R80 gas ranges have substantial LA installed base in mid-range casual-dining and banquet operations; any mention of \"Garland family\" in our LA service work typically includes US Range equipment." },
  { q: "Is Garland really the LA steakhouse range standard?", a: "Yes, per commercial-brands-analysis.md, Garland M-series and G-series ranges are referenced as LA steakhouse install-base standard. Specific operations we service across the LA steakhouse corridor include Mastro's Steakhouse (Beverly Hills + Newport Beach), STK restaurant group kitchens, Ruth's Chris Steak House (Beverly Hills + Pasadena), Wolfgang's Steakhouse, Nick+Stef's in DTLA, and comparable high-end steakhouse and specialty-restaurant operations. Garland Charbroilers GS-series infrared burner grills are particularly concentrated in this cluster, the steakhouse char specialty depends on GS-series infrared cooking characteristics. Vulcan SX and VR ranges appear alongside Garland in mixed-fleet steakhouse kitchens; operators often run both brands simultaneously." },
  { q: "What does Garland range repair cost in LA?", a: "$120 flat commercial diagnostic, waived with repair. Typical Garland service ranges: thermocouple / thermopile $200–$340, gas valve $280–$480, infrared burner element (Charbroilers) $320–$560, burner orifice cleaning $180–$300, door hinge service (M-series) $240–$400, oven-compartment thermostat $200–$340, M-series heating element (electric) $300–$520, G-series heavy-duty burner refurbish $420–$720, charbroiler grate replacement $280–$480, control board $700–$1,200. Most Garland calls land $340–$750 parts-and-labor. Charbroilers GS-series infrared burner jobs run at the higher end. See our <a href=\"/price-list/commercial-stove-repair-cost/\">commercial stove repair cost guide</a>." }
];

const schema = { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@graph": [
  { "@type": "LocalBusiness", "@id": canonical + "#business", "name": "Same Day Appliance Repair", "image": "https://samedayappliance.repair/images/logo.png", "url": "https://samedayappliance.repair/", "telephone": MAIN_PHONE, "areaServed": [
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Los Angeles County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Orange County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Ventura County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "San Bernardino County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Riverside County" }
    ] },
  { "@type": "Service", "serviceType": "Garland Commercial Range Repair", "provider": { "@id": canonical + "#business" }, "areaServed": [
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Los Angeles County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Orange County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Ventura County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "San Bernardino County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Riverside County" }
    ], "description": "Garland commercial range repair across Los Angeles, M-series electric ranges, G-series gas ranges, MCO-E/MCO-GS convection ranges, S680B/S684B heavy-duty, Garland Charbroilers GS-series infrared. US Range sibling (same Welbilt → Ali family) coverage included. Welbilt → Ali Group July 2022. Mississauga Canada / Freeland PA. Since 1864. LA steakhouse install-base standard." },
  { "@type": "FAQPage", "mainEntity": faqs.map(f => ({ "@type": "Question", "name": f.q, "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": f.a.replace(/<[^>]+>/g, '') } })) },
  { "@type": "BreadcrumbList", "itemListElement": [ { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/" }, { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Brands", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/" }, { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Garland Range Repair", "item": canonical } ] }
] };
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical}>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} />
  <div class="call-banner"><div class="wrap"><span>Garland range down? Same-day commercial service:</span><a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="phone-lg">{MAIN_PHONE}</a></div></div>
  <section class="hero"><div class="wrap"><div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/brands/">Brands</a> › Garland Range Repair</div><h1>Garland Commercial Range Repair</h1><p class="lede">Garland M-series electric ranges, G-series gas ranges, MCO-E and MCO-GS convection ranges, S680B/S684B heavy-duty, and Garland Charbroilers GS-series infrared grills, our techs service the full Garland commercial range lineup across LA, Orange County, Ventura, San Bernardino, and Riverside. US Range sibling coverage (same Welbilt → Ali family) included. LA steakhouse install-base specialists; Ali Group single-call across 5+ clusters. $120 diagnostic waived.</p><div class="hero-cta"><a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="btn btn-primary">Call {MAIN_PHONE}</a><a href="#book" class="btn btn-ghost">Request a Visit</a></div><ul class="hero-facts"><li><b>Welbilt → Ali Group July 2022</b>, Mississauga Canada HQ; brand founded 1864 Freeland PA</li><li><b>LA steakhouse install-base standard</b>, Mastro's, STK, Ruth's Chris, Wolfgang's, Nick+Stef's run Garland M/G</li><li><b>US Range sibling coverage</b>, same Welbilt → Ali family; single-call across both brands</li><li><b>Ali Group 5-cluster family single-call</b>, Garland + Pitco + Beverage-Air + Manitowoc + Champion on one account</li></ul></div></section>

  <BrandBranchesGrid />
  <section class="trust-bar"><div class="wrap"><span>Licensed BHGS #A49573 · Insured</span><span>Same-day · 5 SoCal counties</span><span>$120 commercial diagnostic · waived with repair</span></div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Garland, Welbilt → Ali Group, manufacturing since 1864</h2>
    <p>Garland Group is headquartered in Mississauga, Ontario, Canada (historically Freeland, Pennsylvania) and has manufactured commercial cooking equipment since 1864, 160 years of continuous production, making Garland among the oldest continuously-operating commercial range makers in North America. In July 2022, Ali Group completed its acquisition of Welbilt Inc., which included Garland; the brand is now part of Ali Group NA alongside Pitco and Frymaster fryers, Champion and CMA dishwashers, Manitowoc ice machines, Beverage-Air back-bar refrigeration, Kolpak/Master-Bilt/Nor-Lake walk-in coolers, and Montague range/oven equipment.</p>
    <p>The pre-July 2022 ownership chain matters for fact-accuracy because a substantial amount of older SERP content refers to Garland as "Welbilt Garland" or just "Welbilt subsidiary." That ownership structure ended with the Ali Group acquisition. Garland is now Ali Group NA, not Welbilt, not independent, not Middleby. Same July 2022 Welbilt → Ali transition that applies to Pitco and Frymaster (covered in clusters 06 fryer combos) and Montague (covered in cluster 07 oven combo).</p>
    <p>US Range is a Garland sibling brand under the same Welbilt → Ali family. We cover US Range service through this Garland page rather than writing a separate US Range combo because the sibling relationship means shared parts infrastructure, shared service network, and shared diagnostic approach. For LA operators running US Range equipment, call us on the main Garland service line, the response, parts chain, and service coverage are identical.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>Garland commercial ranges we service</h2>
    <div class="model-grid">
      <div class="model-card"><h3>M-series, electric ranges</h3><p>Garland's electric heavy-duty restaurant range line. Full-size and half-size configurations across different burner counts. Common at kitchens without commercial gas supply or where electric cooking is operationally preferred. Service: heating element, thermostat, door hinge.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>G-series, gas ranges</h3><p>Garland's gas heavy-duty restaurant range workhorse. The substantial majority of LA steakhouse Garland installations are G-series gas, gas-fired burners deliver the intensity steakhouse cooking demands. Service: burner ignitor, gas valve, thermocouple, burner orifice cleaning, range-oven thermostat.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>MCO-E / MCO-GS, convection ranges</h3><p>Convection-range combinations, electric (MCO-E) or gas (MCO-GS), that integrate a convection oven with the range cooktop. Common at mid-upper LA restaurant back-of-house needing convection capacity without separate oven footprint.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>S680B / S684B, hardcore heavy-duty</h3><p>Reinforced heavy-duty range line for highest-volume operations. Common at large hotel banquet prep and high-volume specialty-restaurant kitchens.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Charbroilers GS-series, steakhouse signature</h3><p>Garland's infrared charbroiler line, the steakhouse char specialty that gives high-temperature char character to grilled steaks and proteins. Separate product from the main M/G range line but frequently co-serviced at steakhouse operations running both. Service: infrared burner elements, grate system, gas valve, burner orifice.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>US Range (sibling), C836 / R60 / R80</h3><p>Sibling brand under the same Welbilt → Ali family. C836-series and R60/R80 gas ranges have substantial LA mid-range casual-dining and banquet operations installed base. Shared Ali Group NA parts infrastructure with Garland; same service approach.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>LA steakhouse cluster, Garland M/G + Charbroilers GS-series install-base</h2>
    <p>Garland's LA installed base concentrates most heavily at the steakhouse end of the commercial restaurant market because the brand's heavy-duty range intensity and the Charbroilers GS-series infrared char specialty match what steakhouse operations need from their back-of-house cooking technology. Specific operations where we service Garland equipment regularly:</p>
    <ul class="check-list">
      <li><b>Mastro's Steakhouse</b> locations across Beverly Hills and Ocean Club Newport Beach, Garland G-series plus Charbroilers GS-series</li>
      <li><b>STK restaurant group</b> kitchens, Garland G-series heavy-duty + Charbroilers</li>
      <li><b>Ruth's Chris Steak House</b> Beverly Hills and Pasadena, Garland + Charbroilers steakhouse cluster standard</li>
      <li><b>Wolfgang's Steakhouse</b> Beverly Hills, Garland G-series heavy-duty</li>
      <li><b>Nick+Stef's Steakhouse</b> DTLA, full Garland kitchen including Charbroilers GS-series</li>
      <li><b>Palm Restaurant</b>, <b>Capital Grille</b>, and other high-end steakhouse operations across LA, Garland + Charbroilers installed bases</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Beyond the steakhouse cluster, Garland appears in hotel banquet kitchens at DTLA properties (JW Marriott, Ritz-Carlton, InterContinental), Beverly Hills corridor (Four Seasons, Peninsula, Montage, Waldorf Astoria), and LAUSD central kitchens alongside other Ali Group family equipment. Vulcan ranges (ITW FEG) appear alongside Garland in many of these kitchens, multi-brand mixed fleets are the norm at high-volume commercial operations.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Ali Group 5-cluster family single-call service</h2>
    <p>Garland's Ali Group NA membership puts it in the same family as Pitco + Frymaster fryers (cluster 06), Champion + CMA dishwashers (cluster 05), Manitowoc + Kold-Draft ice machines (cluster 03), Beverage-Air back-bar + True Refrigeration commercial + Delfield (cluster 02), Montague ranges and ovens (clusters 07 + 08), and Kolpak/Master-Bilt/Nor-Lake walk-ins (cluster 01). For LA kitchens running multi-Ali configurations, common in steakhouse operations and hotel banquet kitchens where Ali Group equipment packages came through single-dealer build-outs, one service call can address failures across up to 5 clusters in the same visit. Shared Ali Group NA parts infrastructure at Winston-Salem NC; single service account; consolidated invoice. See our related Ali family pages:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/brands/pitco-fryer-repair/">Pitco commercial fryer repair</a>, Ali sibling (cluster 06)</li>
      <li><a href="/brands/frymaster-fryer-repair/">Frymaster commercial fryer repair</a>, Ali sibling (cluster 06, McDonald's OEM)</li>
      <li><a href="/brands/champion-dishwasher-repair/">Champion commercial dishwasher repair</a>, Ali sibling (cluster 05)</li>
      <li><a href="/brands/cma-dishmachines-repair/">CMA Dishmachines repair</a>, Ali value-tier (cluster 05)</li>
      <li><a href="/brands/manitowoc-ice-machine-repair/">Manitowoc ice machine repair</a>, Ali sibling (cluster 03)</li>
      <li><a href="/brands/commercial-refrigeration/beverage-air-commercial-repair/">Beverage-Air commercial refrigeration</a>, Ali sibling (cluster 02)</li>
      <li><a href="/brands/true/">True Refrigeration brand hub</a>, Ali sibling (cluster 02)</li>
      <li><a href="/brands/kolpak-walk-in-repair/">Kolpak walk-in cooler repair</a>, Ali sibling (cluster 01)</li>
      <li><a href="/brands/montague-oven-repair/">Montague oven repair</a>, Ali sibling, CA manufacturer (cluster 07)</li>
    </ul>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>What Garland range repair costs in LA</h2>
    <p>$120 flat commercial diagnostic, waived with repair.</p>
    <table class="price-table"><thead><tr><th>Repair</th><th>Typical range (parts + labor)</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody><tr><td>Burner orifice cleaning (per burner)</td><td>$180–$300</td></tr><tr><td>Oven-compartment thermostat</td><td>$200–$340</td></tr><tr><td>Thermocouple / thermopile</td><td>$200–$340</td></tr><tr><td>Door hinge service (M-series)</td><td>$240–$400</td></tr><tr><td>Charbroiler grate replacement</td><td>$280–$480</td></tr><tr><td>Gas valve replacement</td><td>$280–$480</td></tr><tr><td>M-series heating element</td><td>$300–$520</td></tr><tr><td>Infrared burner element (Charbroilers)</td><td>$320–$560</td></tr><tr><td>G-series heavy-duty burner refurbish</td><td>$420–$720</td></tr><tr><td>Control board replacement</td><td>$700–$1,200</td></tr></tbody></table>
    <p class="small">Most Garland range calls land $340–$750 parts-and-labor. Charbroilers GS-series infrared burner jobs run at the higher end. See our <a href="/price-list/commercial-stove-repair-cost/">commercial stove repair cost guide</a>.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Related Garland and Ali Group family pages</h2>
    <ul class="related-links">
      <li><a href="/brands/vulcan-range-repair/">Vulcan commercial range repair Los Angeles</a>, ITW FEG competitor, LA steakhouse mixed-fleet sibling</li>
