  <section class="section"><div class="wrap narrow"><h2>Garland range repair, frequently asked</h2>{faqs.map(f => <details class="faq"><summary>{f.q}</summary><p set:html={f.a}></p></details>)}</div></section>

  <section id="book" class="cta-bottom"><div class="wrap"><h2>Garland down? Call the branch nearest your kitchen.</h2><p>Same-day in LA, Orange County, Ventura, San Bernardino, and Riverside. $120 commercial diagnostic, waived with repair.</p></div></section>
